        <mxCell id="eng_llama_body" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#3E3853;" value="llama.cpp-omni is OmniInfer&#39;s self-developed framework built on llama.cpp.&lt;br&gt;Optimized for &lt;b&gt;lower latency&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;higher throughput&lt;/b&gt;, and stable long-running local service workloads.&lt;br&gt;Includes &lt;b&gt;TurboQuant-style optimization&lt;/b&gt; work alongside CPU, CUDA, Vulkan, ROCm, Metal, SYCL, and multimodal GGUF support." vertex="1">
